adDetails: Classical - Jazz - Party Music show contact info The Jazz Duo is an experienced piano-guitar group that plays cocktail jazz for parties and classical music for weddings. The Jazz Duo can provide a portable digital piano with speakers and microphone for speeches or announcements. Any size band is available. Songs by Gershwin, Sinatra, Tony Bennett, Michael Buble, Broadway, The Beatles, Coldplay, Elton John, etc.
